# Welcome to Markdown

This is an example page showing how to use Markdown to create content for your website.

## What is Markdown?

Markdown is a lightweight markup language that you can use to add formatting elements to plaintext text documents. Created by John Gruber in 2004, Markdown is now one of the world's most popular markup languages.

## Why use Markdown?

- **Easy to learn and use** - Simple syntax that's quick to master
- **Focus on content** - Write content without worrying about complex formatting  
- **Portable** - Works across many applications and platforms
- **Future-proof** - Plain text format that will never become obsolete

## Formatting Examples

